# Digital Farmers Market — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full-stack **FarmConnect** platform — a Digital Farmers Market where farmers list produce (direct sale or auction) and consumers browse, bid, and buy.

---

## Architecture

```
Digital-Farmers-Market/
├── backend/
│   ├── config/db.js              — Mongoose connection
│   ├── models/                   — User, Product, Bid, Order
│   ├── controllers/              — auth, product, bid, order, admin
│   ├── routes/                   — 5 route files
│   ├── middleware/               — auth.js, errorHandler.js, upload.js
│   └── server.js                 — Express entry point
└── frontend/
    └── src/
        ├── api/axios.js          — JWT interceptor
        ├── context/AuthContext.jsx
        ├── components/common/    — Navbar, CursorGlow
        └── pages/                — 8 pages
```

## Backend Verification

| Endpoint | Status |
|---|---|
| `GET /api/health` | ✅ `{"status":"ok","message":"Digital Farmers Market API running 🌾"}` |
| `POST /api/auth/register` | ✅ 201 with approval message |
| `POST /api/auth/login` | ✅ Returns JWT + user object |
| `GET /api/products` | ✅ Filterable product list |
| `POST /api/bids` | ✅ Min-increment bid validation |
| `POST /api/orders/direct` | ✅ Creates order, reduces stock |

## Frontend Pages

| Page | Status |
|---|---|
| Home | ✅ Hero, stats, categories, features, CTA |
| Login | ✅ Glassmorphism card, JWT login |
| Register | ✅ Role selector, approval notice |
| Marketplace | ✅ Category + price + type + location filters |
| ProductDetail | ✅ Live bid panel (5s refresh) + direct buy |
| FarmerDashboard | ✅ Modal product add + earnings + orders |
| ConsumerDashboard | ✅ Orders + my bids with status |
| AdminDashboard | ✅ Pending approval tab + all users |

## Premium UI Features Implemented

- ✅ Glassmorphism cards with `backdrop-filter: blur(20px)`
- ✅ Floating frosted-glass navbar (top-centered, rounded)
- ✅ Framer Motion page transitions + card hover animations
- ✅ Mouse cursor glow (radial green gradient follows cursor)
- ✅ Gradient backgrounds (emerald-teal, CSS `radial-gradient`)
- ✅ Skeleton loader shimmer effect on data fetches  
- ✅ Toast notifications (styled with glass look via react-hot-toast)
- ✅ Animated modals with `AnimatePresence` + spring physics
- ✅ Live bid auto-refresh every 5 seconds (simulated real-time)
- ✅ Mobile responsive grid (3→2→1 col breakpoints)
- ✅ Google Fonts — Inter + Plus Jakarta Sans

