## Admin Moderation Features
- ✅ **User Management:** Approve/Disapprove users, promote farmers to Admin, and remove users permanently.
- ✅ **Product Moderation:** New products appear in "Reviewing" status. Admins must approve them before they go live.
- ✅ **Status Tracking:** Farmers see "Live", "Reviewing", or "Rejected" status on their dashboard.
- ✅ **Platform Stats:** Real-time tracking of revenue, user counts, and moderation queues.

## Running the Project

```bash
# Backend (Terminal 1)
cd Digital-Farmers-Market/backend
npm run dev        # → http://localhost:5000

# Frontend (Terminal 2)
cd Digital-Farmers-Market/frontend
npm run dev        # → http://localhost:5173
```

> **Note:** Make sure MongoDB is running locally (`mongod`) before starting the backend. The database `digital_farmers_market` is auto-created on first connect.
